          "id": "0bb45b6f2bae9d6fc30c16ec459d6c4f418f1f61",
          "message": "fix(gnovm): add a recursivity limit in stack traces (#4864)\n\nWhen the recursive limit is reached (default: 100), stop detailing the\nobject content, and just return \"...\". It avoids a possible stack\noverflow when tracing deeply nested objects or expressions.\n\nFixes GHSA-x8f6-whgf-9ggf",
